data.description: House will NOT be auctioned. Amazing opportunity right by South Mountain! 4 Beds and 2 Baths in a gated neighborhood with lots of eating and dining only a short drive away. This home has a split Floor Plan with a full master bedroom, full master bathroom with double sinks and walk-in closet. Three bedrooms with all laminated flooring and access to full bathroom. Indoor laundry and 2 car garage with storage area. Awesome and spacious over-sized backyard has plenty of room for lots of uses. This great home has a great layout, lots of space, and tons of potential. No creative financing, no subject-to, no seller carry
